title: How to Make MILLIONS as a College Athlete | Creator Economics Episode #22
description: With recent NCAA NIL rule changes, thousands of student athletes are wondering how to best monetize their name, image, and likeness. Deestroying joins Reed Duchscher on the podcast this week to discuss his Youtube journey after forfeiting his college football scholarship and his advice for college athletes hoping to take advantage of these new NIL opportunities.
dc:creator: Reed Duchscher and Blake Robbins
